{
  "texts": [
    "Translation requires accuracy and reliability, arguably even more when it comes to complex and difficult narratives of human experience.",
    "AI safety and content moderation raises ethical issues regarding the use of LLMs for translation.",
    "Our work facilitates the examination of these ethical issues on real life data.",
    "As LLMs are increasingly incorporated into translation pipelines, it is crucial to understand how these safety mechanisms handle complex accounts from real sources, as opposed to synthetic texts created to test AI models.",
    "However, turning testimonies of contemporary individuals into AI test sets comes with its own set of ethical challenges, such as violations of privacy and consent."
  ]
}